title: Blackhawk (001 - 003) (1987 - 1988)
description:
Blackhawk (001 - 003) (1987 - 1988) 

In 1988, Howard Chaykin revived the Blackhawk Squadron with a more mature reader orientated tone as well as several updates and slight name changes to make the originals less stereotypical as well as some new characters entirely.

This 3 issue prestige mini-series was well received and Chaykin's revised team continued on into Action Comics Weekly and then an ongoing series Blackhawk (1989).
